
Age:16Personality: fun, full of ideas, friendly, music. Gay.
Prologue.
Levi was gay, but he was very good at  hiding it, his parents didn't even suspect anything.
Levi even dated a few girls but never truly loved them.
Levi made the mistake of telling one of the girls, she told everyone.
Everyone mocked him, beat him up. Soon his parents found out about it and were disappointed.
He drifted away he tried to jump of ledge twice but it wasn't high enough.
He is alone.